    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/f265c02689063efc32b60d43b4f368ab.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=230 /></span>  <br>Explore the universe in this single-player cyberpunk adventure, with a little cow that will turn your world upside down. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/42398d3494143dbebc90b51aebe18144.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=140 /></span>  <br><br>There are many popular tales and urban legends about extraterrestrials abducting cows, but what happens to the cows after they’ve been abducted?  <br>On a peaceful planet inhabited by cows that just walk, graze, and fart, an innocent cow is abducted to a strange planet and placed in a prison.  <br>After managing to escape, she begins to explore this new world, looking for ways to return home.  <br>What was once just another cow in the pasture, transforms into an individual with personality, fears, and desires.  <br>Her journey goes beyond the discovery of other worlds: it’s a journey of self-discovery.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/8a390b56908e35d2f2c4a33868d7a23c.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >360º PLATAFORM</h2>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.poster.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.webm?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.mp4?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>Move all around the planet and turn the ceiling into the floor with a gravity-switching mechanic.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT'S IN THIS DEMO?</h2>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.poster.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.webm?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.mp4?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>In this demo, you will get to know Mooh’s home planet and face the very first challenge of all: the first unknown planet.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIX THE SPACESHIP</h2>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.poster.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.webm?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.mp4?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>Find and collect the necessary parts to repair a broken ship and take the character away from there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIMOSAS</h2>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.poster.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.webm?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.mp4?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>Mooh wasn’t the only one abducted! To save other cows, which we affectionately call &quot;mimosas,&quot; you need to find the cells where they are held captive and set them free.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENEMIES AND PUZZLES</h2>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/9987ce191d61331920c3927fc30d3017.poster.avif?t=1727890722\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187180/extras/9987ce191d61331920c3927fc30d3017.webm?t=1727890722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <br>Face the enemies, solve the puzzles of planet 1 and get ready for the challenges ahead! Mooh is just getting started.",
